# Tech Stack and FastAPI

- Python 3.11+, FastAPI, pytest, `pydantic-settings`, `pyproject.toml` packaging.
- Webhook endpoints respond quickly; AI CLI work runs in background jobs, not inside webhook handlers.
- Centralize env vars in `config.py` or a settings object. Document new env vars and file-based settings in README.
- Before tests or server commands, use the `remote-coder` Conda environment: `conda run -n remote-coder ...`.
- No fixed lint/format command in this repo; follow existing code style.
